snippet.title: United Season 3: GEMMED - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
United Season 3 is here. The Island has been Gemmed, and your favorite POIs have been altered. Lock on to objects with the Homing Attack, or Spray enemies with the new Gemmed Weapons!
